Package soffico.customerapi.channel

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CustomChannelInstance
    Base interface that has to be implemented by all user defined channel instances
    CustomOutboundAdapter
    This interface has to be implemented by all user defined channels that should be used as an outbound channel
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChannelConfiguration
    Base object that defines to root object for all user-defined channel configuration settings.
    ChannelConfigurationAdapter
    Internal class that maps channel configuration from orchestra domain to customer api domain.
    ChannelInboundAdapter
    Base class for a user defined inbound channels.
    ChannelOutboundAdapter
    Baseclass for a user defined outbound channel.
    ChannelPanelAdapter
    Adapter class that maps the customer channel ui interfaces to the internal orchestra ui structures.
    ChannelStateEntry
    This class modells an information item that holds some information for the current channel state
    OrchestraTransaction
    This class is a handle to the internal orchestra transaction mechanism.
    PropertyDeclaration
    This class is used for the definition of the propertie given as request or response parameters to a channel invocation
    SynchronousResult
    This class holds the result of the synchonous execution of an inbound channel invocation
